description:
UeCA: Table storing User Equipment Cell Association (UeCA) data, including timestamp, area name, cell ID, and unique identifiers for the UE and measurement.
dateTime: Timestamp of the UeCA measurement.
Area_Name: Name of the area where the UE is associated.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell the UE is connected to.
Id2: Redundant/Alternative cell ID.
Id3:  Generic identifier (appears to be always '1' in this sample).
vsDataType: Type of data; specifically, UeCA data.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the UeCA data format.
UeCA.ueCAId: Unique identifier for this specific UeCA record.
